channel.title: Comments on: VIDEO: I Blame Coco “Self-Machine”

item.title: By: K
item.dc:creator: K
item.description: WTF?! You are so right. I'm generally all about the electronic bleeps, but the sparse instrumentation from the demos really fits her voice. This just sounds over-produced and kitsch.
